electric_blast_furnace_0: 每超过配方温度[c/FFFFFF:900K][c/AAAAAA:，耗能均将乘以][c/FFFFFF:95%%][c/AAAAAA:（不计超频）。]
electric_blast_furnace_1: 每超过配方温度[c/FFFFFF:1800K][c/AAAAAA:，将一次超频的效率变为][c/FFFFFF:100%%][c/AAAAAA:（无损超频）。]
